common_issues.title: Pieces Core Services Fails to Open Due to WebSocket Error
common_issues.description: Multiple users across macOS and Windows are unable to open Pieces Core Services.  The error is a WebSocketException with a 404 HTTP status code, indicating the service is not running or accessible at the expected endpoint (http://127.0.0.1:39300). Check if Pieces Core Services is running, firewall settings, and network connectivity. Reinstallation may be necessary.
